title: #92Noon! Montage/Bercich/JG/Siny/Vikes & Thielen Talker
description: Montage, followed by Pete Bercich in studio! JG on Gophers midway through, with the Border Battle & Dave Sinykin wrapping up the 2nd hour. On how many teams would Adam Thielen be the #1 receiver? Calls to close!
